    "description": "SSC Tube invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Senior Teacher at our Pimpri-Chinchwad location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout SSC Tube:\nSSC Tube is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct doubt-clearing sessions and remedial classes for weak students\n• Coordinate with academic counselors for student career guidance\n• Develop and deliver engaging lesson plans for students\n• Participate in teacher training and professional development programs\n• Conduct parent-teacher meetings and update parents on student performance\n• Create curriculum-aligned learning materials and assessments\n• Support students with special educational needs\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in LMS Platforms\n• Proficiency in CBSE/ICSE Standards\n• Proficiency in Data Analysis\n• Proficiency in Educational Technology\n• Proficiency in E-learning\n• Proficiency in Research Skills\n• Proficiency in Student Assessment\n• Proficiency in Zoom/Teams\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pimpri-Chinchwad, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with SSC Tube!",
